      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how none of this actually matters. like, we're just biological accidents on a rock that's eventually going to be swallowed by the sun, and then even the stars will die. it feels so stupid to keep trying, you know? to keep struggling and hurting just to maintain a consciousness that is ultimately going nowhere. it feels like such a waste of energy.",
